This adapter interfaces to the Leica DMSTC XY stage.  Connect the DMSTC to an available serial port on your computer.   You will need to define the ''Hub'' device, and assign the correct serial port to it. 

IMPORTANT!: During Micro-Manager startup the stage moves to the top left corner and then to the bottom right to define the origin and end points of travel.  MAKE SURE THE ENTIRE RANGE OF STAGE TRAVEL IS FREE AND CLEAR BEFORE INITIALIZATION!


